              <span style='font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;background:#FCF8E3;'>Collection, recording, systematization, accumulation, storage, destruction and depersonalization of personal data</span>
            </li>
            <li style='margin:0cm;font-size:16px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;color:#212529;'><span
                style='font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;background:#FCF8E3;'>Sending newsletters to an email address</span>
